# HROBOT Git ignore rules
# 默认策略：上传源码与文档，不上传本地 HR 数据、密钥、缓存和打包产物。

# Python / runtime caches
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/

# Virtual environments / local dependencies
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/

# Local secrets and environment files
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.p12
*.pfx

# Local editor / OS noise
.cursor/
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Logs and temporary files
*.log
*.tmp
*.temp
*.bak
*.swp
*.swo
tmp/
temp/
logs/

# Build / package outputs
build/
dist/
packages/
*.zip
*.7z
*.rar
*.tar
*.tar.gz

# Local server / process artifacts
*.pid
server-debug*.log

# Brand-specific local assets and generated design notes
# 公开仓库建议不要上传公司 VI、旧品牌素材或历史设计提示词。
assets/brand/
docs/brand-vi.md
docs/superpowers/

# HR data, uploaded files, generated reports, and local app state
# 如需上传演示数据，请先单独放入已脱敏的 demo/sample 目录，再手动放行。
data/*
!data/.gitkeep
!data/README.md
!data/demo/
!data/demo/**
!data/samples/
!data/samples/**

# Optional: keep non-sensitive template directory only after manual review.
# 如果确认模板不含真实员工/公司信息，可删除下面两行的注释并提交模板。
# !data/templates/
# !data/templates/**
